				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Before you try pulling a lvl 65 high risk....<a name="55021"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 3 04 9:30 PM</span></td>
